| ID | Finding | Severity |
|----|---------|----------|
| F1 | `/doey-instant-task` emits subject `new_task` not handled by Taskmaster → silent drop | P0 |
| F2 | Review → Deploy path conflicts: `deploy_request` vs `deployment_request` vs `review_passed` — routing ambiguous | P0 |
| F3 | Coordinator prompt bloat (cross-ref W1·F1.1) — amplifies every coordination turn | P0 |
