| F10 | Phases serialize even when subtasks are independent — phase-graph not used | P1 |
| F12 | Stale-detection writes alerts but does not trigger respawn — manual intervention required | P1 |
| F16 | `on-pre-tool-use.sh` size affects latency (cross-ref W2·P0-2) — shrink for speed, not tokens | P0 |
